videos.description: Iowa's Nick Easley fumbles into the endzone for a touchback negating a touchdown for Iowa.
videos.headline: North Texas dodges a bullet

videos.description: Jeffery Wright's gallops 41-yards to give North Texas a 7-0 lead.
videos.headline: North Texas HB breaks tackle and runs for TD

videos.description: T.J. Hockenson catches an 8-yard  pass off a deflection for touchdown to tie the game.
videos.headline: Iowa ties the game

videos.description: Joshua Jackson flies off the edge and blocks the North Texas field goal to keep the score tied at 7.
videos.headline: Iowa blocks FG

videos.description: TD pitch and catch gives North Texas the led.
videos.headline: North Texas strikes back

videos.description: Iowa head coach Kirk Ferentz talks adjustments for the second half against North Texas.
videos.headline: Ferentz gives his thoughts on the first half

videos.description: Iowa's Nathan Stanley's second touchdown pass of the game gives Iowa the lead again.
videos.headline: Iowa reclaims the lead

videos.description: Ivory Kelly-Martin scores on a 2-yard run to push the lead to 10 for Iowa.
videos.headline: Iowa punches another one in for a TD

videos.description: Ivory Kelly-Martin scores his second touchdown of the game to finish off North Texas.
videos.headline: Iowa puts it away
